1. Real-Time Delivery Tracking: Stay informed about the status of your deliveries with real-time updates. Track the location of your package and receive notifications oits progre.

2. Delivery Management: Schedule, reschedule, and cancel deliveries directly from the app. Easily manage your delivery preferences and communication with thdelivery personnel.

3. Communication Channels**: Directly communicate with the delivery team through the app, allowing you to provide instructions, address changes, or any other important information.

4. Delivery History: Access a comprehensive history of your past deliveries, including tracking details, delivery times, and any relevant notes.

5. Notifications and Alerts: Receive timely notifications about your delivery status, including estimated arrival times, delays, or any other important updat.
